KlipFolio,is,a,desktop,dashboard,for,Microsoft,Windows,The,program,uses,different,Klips,to,display,information,that,a,user,chooses,to,have,in,front,of,themselves,at,all,times,There,are,over,four,thousand,different,Klips,which,display,information,like,the,weather,conditions,e,mail,news,comic,strips,and,business,information